                  <p>Photocopies of the indices from the six volumes are gathered together to facilitate usability.  Each handwritten index provides an alphabetical sequence of names and topics with notation of relevant pages in the volume. This folder also contains an alphabetical index of clergymen/missionaries mentioned in the volumes, which was prepared by the vendor of the collection, and the vendor's description of the collection.</p>
