                  <p>Volume 1 contains 868 pages, including 349 letters, and has a detailed index at the end of the volume.  Letters in this volume that were written by Sanford Richardson date from 1857 July 17 to 1859 December 31 and documents received by Richardson date from 1857 March 24 to 1860 March 20. The volume includes a few press-copy illustrations by Richardson related to the Arabkir mission.</p>
                  <p>Prominent correspondents in Volume 1 include Rufus Anderson, Herbert Morton Barnum, Harrison Gray Otis Dwight, William Goodell, Cyrus Hamlin, Elias Riggs, Henry Van Lennep, and George Washburn.</p>
